citation: Pollution of Waters by Oil and Noxious Substances Amendment Regulations 2008 (Rescinded) (Tas)
text:
Pollution of Waters by Oil and Noxious Substances Amendment Regulations 2008 (Rescinded)

This Statutory Rule has been rescinded.

1. (Rescinded)
    The Pollution of Waters by Oil and Noxious Substances Amendment Regulations 2008 have been rescinded by Schedule 2 to the Redundant Legislation Repeal Act 2016
